DARKROCK (V.O.)
This time it's exceptional.  I mean no harm.

TONI
No, dude, this trick won't ever work, alright?

SAYLOR
Ahem?

TONI
Can you hear her?  Watch her repeating what I said!

DARKROCK (V.O.)
Ah, Saylor, at last!

SAYLOR
Did you miss me?

DARKROCK (V.O.)
Ah it was a while, don't you think?

SAYLOR
Incalculable?

Silence of unamusement.

SAYLOR (CONT'D)
For me, it felt like yesterday.  What do you want?

DARKROCK (V.O.)
I offer cooperation.

SAYLOR
Hah!  You?  Cooperation?  We're not cooperating with you.  End of discussion.

DARKROCK (V.O.)
Jenesis.

SAYLOR
