DARKROCK (V.O.)
She exists, you know.

SAYLOR
Then I can make her stop existing.  By living a different life.  Rewriting the history, because I'm a history.  Simple as that!

DARKROCK (V.O.)
Anyway, that's between you two to figure out.  I'm here for another reason.

SAYLOR
You said she's mad.
(to herself)
Well, she always had been.

