(to both DARKROCK and SAYLOR)
I'm not interrupting your top secret convo.  Still, I know everything that comes next.  You both know why.  Mainly, good memory.  So, no secrets for me.  I'll just allow your plans to happen.  Maybe you'll reach some progress.  You might even surprise me.

SAYLOR
