JENESIS (V.O.)
I had the same thought in your age.  And I had it for a while.  Until I've started seeing a bigger picture.  And you saw it already, but you're not ready to accept it yet.

SAYLOR
So, what's new in your... rearrangements?  Not just in a cosmic sense, but in your head.

JENESIS (V.O.)
